gpsrecorder (0.1.144) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added : Unit conversion settings for distances and speed.
  * Modified : Better handling of snapped points in GPX exporter.
  * Modified : Setup system time only once per application instance.
  * Modified : 'Point name' dialog now has shorter description so it is not chopped anymore.
  * Modified : Replaced 'browse' icons to be a little bit more intuitive.

 -- Jean-Charles Lefebvre <gpsrecorder@jcl.name>  Tue, 17 Aug 2010 23:40:59 +0200

